1> List all running VMs:
   virsh list --all

2> Check the status of a specific VM:
   virsh domstate <vm_name>

3> Get detailed information about a specific VM:
   virsh dominfo <vm_name>

4> Get IP Address of the VM:
   virsh domifaddr <vm_name>

5> Delete the VM:
   virsh shutdown <vm_name>
   virsh undefine <vm_name>
